body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Science & Research     Prenest Closures              Prenest Closures         Three American oystercatcher eggs on a nest National Park Service   The ORV Management Plan for Cape Hatteras National Seashore states that prints closures for American oystercatchers, piping plovers, and/ or colonial waterbirds will be in place by March 15 of each year.
